These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: rowing, cycling, water-polo
1. Sport:cycling is on the right of Sport:water-polo##1
2. Sport:rowing is on the far right##1
3. Sport:rowing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling | rowing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: raspberry, nectarine, pineapple
1. Food:nectarine is in an odd position##4
2. Food:raspberry is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | raspberry | pineapple | nectarine |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: card-games, collecting, fishing
1. Hobby:collecting is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:collecting is on the left or right of Hobby:fishing##3
3. Hobby:fishing is on the right of Hobby:collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | card-games | collecting | fishing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
